<h1>Data Deletion Request</h1>
<p class="small">Last updated: 2026-04-20</p>

<div class="card">
    <p>
        You can request deletion of TwitchMiniChat app-related data associated with your use of the app.
    </p>
</div>

<h2>How to request deletion</h2>
<p>
    Email: <a href="mailto:[unouidol.interactive@gmail.com]?subject=TMC%20Data%20Deletion%20Request"></a>
</p>

<h2>Please include</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Your Twitch username</li>
    <li>Any relevant profile or account identifiers, if known</li>
    <li>A short statement that you are requesting deletion of app-related data</li>
</ul>

<h2>What may be deleted</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Push registration data</li>
    <li>Stored app-related profile mappings</li>
    <li>Other app-related server-side data associated with your request, where applicable</li>
</ul>

<h2>Retention exceptions</h2>
<p>
    Some limited records may be retained for a short period where reasonably necessary for
    security, abuse prevention, fraud prevention, moderation review, audit, or legal compliance.
</p>

<h2>Response timing</h2>
<p>
    Deletion requests are reviewed and processed within a reasonable timeframe.
</p>
